{"type":"text","timestamp":1775863700238,"sessionID":"ses_28648f112ffezeBig0vH7hGGOs","part":{"id":"prt_d79b988b2001IRVaRBDVXUzt9D","messageID":"msg_d79b97ffa001AaDNKsz9NhNyQe","sessionID":"ses_28648f112ffezeBig0vH7hGGOs","type":"text","text":"Done! I've written the `proposal.md` for AR-019 (CLI õ║īĶ┐øÕłČÕģźÕÅŻ) in `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-019/proposal.md`.\n\nThe proposal covers:\n\n1. **4 CLI Binaries**:\n   - `agentd` - Kubernetes controller (existing)\n   - `picod` - PicoD HTTP daemon for code execution\n   - `agentcube` - Main CLI tool for managing AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter resources\n   - `agentcube-admin` - Administrative CLI for cluster-wide operations\n\n2. **Key Features**:\n   - Full CRUD operations for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter CRDs\n   - Exec/logs/describe commands for debugging\n   - Multiple output formats (table, json, yaml)\n   - Cleanup and diagnostics admin tools\n   - Integration with generated client-go library\n\n3. **Structure**: Includes purpose, scope, current state analysis, proposed changes with code examples, impact analysis, alternatives considered, testing strategy, and acceptance criteria following the existing proposal format.","time":{"start":1775863700237,"end":1775863700237}}}
